All Implemented Interfaces:
Schema<Map<String,V>>
public class StringMapSchema<V>
extends MapSchema<String,V>

A schema for a Map with String keys. The key and value can be null (depending on the particular map impl).

Author:
David Yu
Date created:
Jun 25, 2010
